{"tid":1007943,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖必入] 一人一個離地嘅屋苑新年佈置","createTime":"2019-02-04T06:29:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T06:33:14.000Z","uid":230399,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3532e712238d2483880b7f6890c1cd47acbdd310","tid":1007943,"uid":230399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T06:29:30.000Z","msg":"我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話說我屋苑每年大時大節都會有啲騎呢佈置，整到天花龍鳳都算乸門，但今次⋯⋯我真係要爆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FvYzbU4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFvYzbU4.png&h=da4644c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每日一放學翻去拍卡嘅時候，最矚目嘅一定係食蕉叔叔個更位，果刻我覺得自己好似行緊入靈堂一鳩樣，有幾次差啲有衝動想黎翻個一躹躬佢。個食蕉日日一碌木咁坐係渡，目無表情，唔乸知仲以為奠緊佢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pWaBqgz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpWaBqgz.png&h=977f3170&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最乸離奇係有個corner 放咗個神台係渡。係就係有齊啲金元寶，但無乸乸整2隻核突公仔，睇就睇落想同我拜個年姐，不過⋯⋯我望多2眼，真係覺得無一個主題比冥婚更加適合<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gOoCUaJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgOoCUaJ.png&h=e2da57e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(你睇下佢2個衰樣) <br />\n<br />\n唔知你哋屋苑啲佈置有冇咁爆，大家不妨黎個pk<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔夠你爆，你最爆就正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n爆過你啦7頭 就負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fbc273d5925d459e8b3e7ba40bb29d56b19181f","tid":1007943,"uid":186194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T06:32:10.000Z","msg":"咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁大個神枱 裝飾黎架？"},{"pid":"9672c3a310ef4ed779be5fb2a507fabd1130128a","tid":1007943,"uid":212642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T06:33:14.000Z","msg":"咒人去死咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}